Package: stdiversity
Type: Package
Title: Spatial temproal diversity of raster data 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christian Rossi
Maintainer: Christian Rossi <christian.rossi@nationalpark.ch>
Description: The package allows to calculate spectral/functional diversity from multi-temporal raster 
   files and the contribution of different components as proposed by Rossi et al. (2020). 
   A map with the contribution of each pixel to diversity can be created.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    raster,
    rgdal
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
URL: https://github.com/RossiBz/stdiversity
BugReports: https://github.com/RossiBz/stdiversity/issues
